4:
...I wonder if someone will come for
me tonight.
7:
Someone who would become the
same as I...
15:
Yes. I'm sorry to have called you out
here for this...
20:
...Vampires are those things that
suck people's blood, right? And
they're immortal, hate the sun... and
all that?
24:
And their victims become their
followers... as well as vampires in
their own right.
28:
...That is what I've heard. The
vampire has apparently taken up
residence in the castle alone, and
has been difficult to deal with...
31:
Could I ask for your help with this?
I'd... rather not deal with the trouble
of my sister finding out.
34: Oh, okay? Sure, we'll go check it out.
39:
Huh... Guess vampires really do
exist...
42:
Watch yourselves, you two. I have
faced vampires before, and their
power is not to be underest—
52:
Wh-what was that unenthusiastic
voice just now?
56:
Heh-heh-heh-heh... Welcome,
humans! B-behold, the abyssal
night! I-I am...
60: W-wait! What was my line again?!
65:
Behold, I am the ruler of the abyssal
night and exalted noble of the
undead! I am the vampire, Lumira!
68:
P-perhaps I will suck your blood and
turn you into my followers!
72:
Urk! I knew this would happen... Do
not let your guard down, Alk!
84:
Wh-why? B-because, I... You know...
If we're not the "same," then I...
93:
Ah! B-but, if you guys don't want to
go through with it, I won't force you,
of course...
111:
A-are you sure? Really?! You won't
be a human anymore!
120:
I-I'm really going to bite you! Y-you
can't go back on this, you know!
133: I-I can't do it! I can't suck your blood!
138:
It would hurt, you know?! Being a
vampire is hard, too! I want you to
look out for yourself more!
149:
So... You're saying you just decided
to live here since you thought the
castle was abandoned. Does that
mean you've never bitten anyone
before?
152:
Th-that's right... I've been getting by
on tomato juice...
157:
I can see you aren't hostile to us, so
allow me to ask you something. Why
do you want followers?
160:
The vampires I defeated in the past
were trying to create an army of
undead. If you intend to do the
same—
164:
A-an army? I don't wanna make
anything scary like that! Not me!
167:
Not you? In that case, did another
vampire order you to—
175:
I j-just wanted someone else like me
around! I've been alone forever!
177:
I used to be human until I suddenly
got turned into a vampire. I don't
have any memory of being human
at all!
179:
The one who turned me into a
vampire in the first place suddenly
vanished, and all that was left
behind for me was this book...
184:
How to make followers...
Blood-sucking? Vampires... conduct
themselves with elegance? Is THAT
what you're doing?
188:
I-I want to get help from other
vampires, but I have no idea where
they might be.
191:
I also don't know how much I might
scare people if I stepped into a
regular town, and going out in the
daytime makes my skin get all itchy!
194:
Huh... Sounds like things have been
really rough for you...
199:
I apologize for our rudeness. We
didn't realize the situation you're in...
203:
Y-you don't need to apologize! It's
true that I want followers...
207:
I-I'm sorry. I've been going on and
on about myself, haven't I? You just
want me to leave, right?
211:
I'll leave right away! Just gotta grab
my coffin... Oh, and my tomato juice
too—
214:
N-no, wait! It doesn't seem like
you've got anywhere else to go...
217:
Are you okay with not having any
followers?
222:
...N-no, not really... So I guess I've
gotta go looking elsewhere—
233:
You might be able to find followers
on other worlds.
237:
B-but... To make a follower, she'd
have to... Well, maybe if there was
mutual agreement? Perhaps a
contract or something?
242:
Th-that would still leave us with the
same problem we started with!
She'd be turning people into
vampires!
253: I-I want to go with you!
256:
I don't really know what to do, but I
just don't want to be alone anymore.
So, please—
269:
Eh? Huh?! Were those people
humans? Did I see machines?!
272:
There are lots of different people
around here. Maybe some of them
would be happy to become your
followers?
276:
Thank you, everyone! I'll do my best
to find someone who'll do it!
280:
Y-you there! Wanna be my... Uh...
W-won't you be mine?
